Usage: add_oa_library_property [-help] -lib <libName>} -name <prop_name>
                               -type {boolean integer float string}
                               -value <propValue>

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-lib <libName>}                          # Name of OpenAccess library to add
                                         # the property to. (string, required)
-name <prop_name>                        # Name of property to create.
                                         # (string, required)
-type {boolean integer float string}     # Type of property to create
                                         # (enum, required)
-value <propValue>                       # Value of the property to set. Value
                                         # is interpretted from the input
                                         # string and converted to the specifed
                                         # type  (string, required)